      "description": "Rice blast is one of the most destructive diseases of rice. It causes lesions on leaves, stems, peduncles, panicles, seeds, and roots.",
      "management": [
        "Use resistant varieties.",
        "Avoid excessive nitrogen fertilizer.",
        "Keep field flooded (blast thrives in dry soil conditions).",
        "Apply fungicides like Tricyclazole or Isoprothiolane if severe."
      ]
    },
    {
