        "leaf_yellow_orange_margins",
        "leaf_milky_ooze",
        "leaf_drying_wilt"
      ],
      "description": "Causes wilting of seedlings (Kresek) and yellowing and drying of leaves. The disease creates lesions that start at the leaf margin.",
      "management": [
        "Use resistant varieties (most effective).",
        "Ensure proper field drainage.",
        "Avoid nitrogen fertilizer during outbreaks.",
        "Keep fields clean of weeds."
      ]
    },
    {
