      "symptoms": [
        "stem_dead_heart",
        "panicle_white_head",
        "stem_holes_frass"
      ],
      "description": "Larvae bore into the stem. In the vegetative stage, the central leaf whorl dies (Dead Heart). In the reproductive stage, panicles remain empty and white (White Head).",
